{"tid":349083,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 北 京 演 唱 會 西 班 牙 籍 老 公 抱 囡 囡 上 台 送 驚 喜","createTime":"2017-08-06T09:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T15:33:55.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c64661c9537524c731fc71e757fff013767ae82a","tid":349083,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪(GiGi)噚晚喺北京舉行《好時辰》part 2 演唱會，其間佢嘅西班牙籍老公Sergio就抱住囡囡Sofia上台，一家三口喺台上互動，認真溫馨！而GiGi見到囡囡Sofia，佢就即時蹲低同囡囡傾計，而Sofia雖然只有兩歲多，但全不怯場，完全遺傳咗媽媽嘅風範。<br />\n<br />\n除咗老公帶埋囡囡去北京支持GiGi嘅演唱會，佢嘅好姊妹李心潔同許茹芸都專訪去咗北京支持佢，兩個好姊妹都分別係微博貼圖留言支持佢。李心潔留言話：「入行20年，我們這些姊妹兼小歌迷和她一起回顧了許多經典歌曲，在她感性的分享裡濕了眼眶，在她深情的演唱裡感受她20年來走過的那些起起伏伏的心路歷程，在她努力揮動身體的舞蹈中狂歡。」而心潔仲話：「Sofia的出現簡直就是當晚的大禮！天真，可愛，單純像極了Gigi！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，許茹芸就係微博留言話，其實除咗佢同李心潔，佢哋都有喺手機連上楊采妮，一齊聽GiGi唱歌，真係好鬼感動呢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170806/large/1501999017_acae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170806%2Flarge%2F1501999017_acae.jpg&h=de57c65e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170806/large/1501999019_92f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170806%2Flarge%2F1501999019_92f2.jpg&h=8b988cef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18e6ad63abbbf5a36a804b7aa550b3d2cf4758f0","tid":349083,"uid":2676,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"混血混到咁柒"},{"pid":"34d1d04ae6c2c2690a12c977c50ed412a6ad3c1d","tid":349083,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73d7626f67cef36fec56c39eeb0f123ba1b2900","tid":349083,"uid":3138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:2